530
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:57,900
so different.

531
00:37:58,400 --> 00:38:00,100
It's been hard to adjust.

532
00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:02,200
Actually, for a minute there,

533
00:38:02,200 --> 00:38:04,500
I thought you might choose to stay in the colony.

534
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,200
But, Crane...

535
00:38:10,900 --> 00:38:12,300
believe me...

536
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:15,900
when I say that you belong in Sleepy Hollow.

537
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:20,700
In the here and now.

538
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:28,200
Well...

539
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:31,200
What do you say we go home then?

540
